		<title>Only the ECB can make it a bank run: James Saft</title>
		<link>http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/17/us-column-markets-saft-idUSBRE84G0LK20120517?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=everything&amp;virtualBrandChannel=11563</link>
