		<title>An ungovernable slump: James Saft</title>
		<link>http://blogs.reuters.com/james-saft/2012/05/08/an-ungovernable-slump-james-saft/</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.reuters.com/james-saft/2012/05/08/an-ungovernable-slump-james-saft/#comments</comments>
